post_survey.music_making: I played in high school band. Listen to the radio and music almost daily. I did some singing in school. Played in band post graduation of high school for some parades locally. Helped teach kids to read music and helped learn to play instruments as well. Always had a love for music.
post_survey.activities: drive, clean, computer work, need motivation
post_survey.habit_change: They have remained fairly the same over the course of my life.
post_survey.habits: I like music I can relate to and understand. I choose classical or instrumental if I want some background without words for focusing. Occasionally I will seek a certain type of music based on my mood. I have always enjoyed music and find myself tapping to the beat many times. Enjoyed listening to the kids in band.
